---
title: Brie and Fig Pork Chops with Potato Coins and Pecan Salad
description: Rich and buttery brie cheese works together with sweet fig spread to amp up the flavour of juicy bone-in pork chops. Finished in a savoury pan sauce and paired with roasted  potatoes and a fresh salad, say hello to a restaurant-quality meal made right in your own kitchen !
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cotelettes-de-porc-au-brie-et-aux-figues-86818bc7.jpg
